title: Grant Kekana
text: Grant Kekana (born 31 October 1992) is a South African <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er who plays as a <a href="defender%20%28football%29">defender</a> for <a href="Mamelodi%20Sundowns%20F.C.">Mamelodi Sundowns</a> in the <a href="Premier%20Soccer%20League">Premier Soccer League</a>.
